
# Project Architecture

We'll start with **one Producer** and **one Consumer**.

```text
                    Customer

                       |

              POST /api/orders

                       |

              Order Service (Producer)

                       |

               Kafka Topic (orders)

                       |

             Payment Service (Consumer)
```

Later we'll add:

* Inventory Service
* Notification Service
* Shipping Service
* Fraud Detection Service

